---
import Section from "./Section.astro";
---

<Section>
  <div class="py-24 reveal" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-end justify-between gap-12">

      <div class="space-y-5 max-w-2xl">
        <p class="section-label text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em]" style="color: var(--accent);">
          About
        </p>
        <h2
          class="font-serif font-normal leading-[1.08]"
          style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem); color: var(--text);"
        >
          Most businesses are<br />solving the wrong problem.
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 max-w-lg text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-muted);">
          <p>
            Most businesses have goals. Most have plans. Very few have made a real strategic
            choice — a clear answer to where exactly they compete and how exactly they beat
            the competition there.
          </p>
          <p>
            The gap between those two things is where most budgets disappear, most campaigns
            underperform, and most growth stalls.
          </p>
          <p>
            Occulta works at that gap. Strategy built as an integrated set of choices.
            Brand built to create pricing power and market presence over time. Marketing
            calibrated to activate both — with the measurement infrastructure to know
            what's working.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you're running hard but not pulling away, the problem is probably upstream
            of the tactics. That's the conversation worth having.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="shrink-0">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Start the conversation</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
